libzip 1.11.4

Upstream: https://libzip.org/
Tarball:  https://libzip.org/download/libzip-1.11.4.tar.gz
SHA256:   82e9f2f2421f9d7c2466bbc3173cd09595a88ea37db0d559a9d0a2dc60dc722e

Layout
------
  src/          — contents of upstream lib/ plus two generated files:
                  zip_err_str.c  (from cmake/GenerateZipErrorStrings.cmake)
                  zipconf.h      (from cmake-zipconf.h.in)
  src/config.h  — HyperXTalk-specific portable config (NOT upstream).
                  Preprocessor-branched on _WIN32 / __APPLE__ / __linux__;
                  replaces the cmake-generated config.h so we can build
                  without running cmake at engine-build time.
  include/      — public headers (zip.h + zipconf.h), copied from src/
                  for consumers (revzip) that only want the public API.

Optional features excluded from libzip.gyp: bzip2, xz (lzma), zstd,
winzip AES, OpenSSL, CommonCrypto, GnuTLS, mbed TLS. The engine does
not link against any of them.
